data.description: Awesome 7.09 acre Hobby Farm! Enjoy the peace & quiet of living in this Lovely Completely Remodeled country home! 2 bedrooms on main level & 2 in walkout basement. New dishwasher, New HVAC, New toilets, New baseboards & trim, New LVT Plank flooring on top floor, New roof in 2019, New Finished concrete floors in basement, Second living room downstairs with wood burning stove & hookups for optional second kitchen, perfect for extended family or guests. Office area & bonus room in basement. Whole house (outbuilding included) fire & security system. Above ground pool with deck, furniture & umbrellas, 4 car 40x20 red iron metal building, 24x32 heated & cooled woodworking shop, 20x14 shed, fenced chicken coop, 27x18 rabbit barn with hanging cages, fully outfitted for breeding. Loafing shed with 3 stalls one extended out for pigs, one access for horses to fenced field. 4-6 person steel storm shelter. Fenced garden with deer netting, shooting range, & deer stand for hunting. Two 50 amp RV hookups. This property has it all!
